Text: EMTA Membership Infoyou for your interest in pursuing membership with our association To answer your question about Website Access ALL categories of membership are given access to the Members Only area As you mention in your latest voice mail message since wekeep missing each other I thought I would send you some information with this email Please review the attached brief description of EMTA and theservices we provide You may alsowish to forward your mailing addressto me so that I can send youour entire Membership Kit which includes some additional information including our latest Quarterly bulletin and Annual Report In the meantime if you have any further questions please do not hesitate to contact me either via email or phone Suzette Ortiz Memduesdoc Memformdoc Emtadoc
